works.description: The moment I saw the new Mercedes-Benz Aria Concept, it somehow reminded me of the sleek SilverFlow concept we saw back in 2007. Designed by Macedonian design student Slavche Tanevski for the year 2030, the Mercedes-Benz Aria Concept electric luxury car draws inspiration from the flying hair and musical instruments. The concept took shape at the Mercedes-Benz Design Studio under the valued supervision of the company’s design chiefs and designers.
